ActImmigration and Refugee Protection Act
PrecisOrder fixing the remuneration of PAULA LYNNE THOMPSON, full time member and Assistant Deputy Chairperson of the Immigration and Refugee Board (Ottawa District Office) for the period she is acting as Deputy Chairperson of the Refugee Appeal Division, effective June 11, 2018, until such time as a new Deputy Chairperson of the Refugee Appeal Division is designated.
